     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Visual Studio Professional theme. A
         warm-toned dark palette distinct from the VS2022Dark variant, with
         slightly higher contrast borders and a richer tab strip appearance.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in VisualStudioTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

